name: 404-redirect-yourls
body:
### 404-Redirect for YOURLS
This plugin's aim is to try to reproduce the 404 function of a web server.
Also setting a 404 header for search engine's bots.

```
$ git clone https://github.com/1Conan/404-redirect-YOURLS.git
```


### Authors and Contributors
@1Conan


### Support or Contact
For bugs and issues, please open an issue in the github repo.
To contact me, simply e-mail me at admin[at]1conan.com
